Detailed Description

Interface for Adafruit's BMP180 sensor board.

This class and its implementation is mostly based on Kevin Townsend's work for Adafruit Industries (Adafruit_BMP085_Unified class).

See also:
http://www.adafruit.com/products/1603#Technical_Details
http://learn.adafruit.com/bmp085/wiring-the-bmp085
